<TEXT>
   Actress Leslie Easterbrook says she's
trying to break a career mold of playing what she called comic
bimbos and move into other roles.
   Easterbrook is best known for her portrayal of a tough but
attractive blonde in the ``Police Academy'' films.
   ``I started to think, `Hey, I can stand up on my own two feet.'
Why do I have to wait for someone else to offer me a job _ to
