<HEAD>Cuba Train Accident Injures 100</HEAD>
<DATELINE>MEXICO CITY (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   A train derailed in eastern Cuba and about
100 passengers were injured, Cuba's official Prensa Latina news
